{"tid":22553,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁 詠 琪 肚 凸 凸 否 認 再 懷 孕","createTime":"2016-12-04T13:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T14:49:15.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52a2cea22e4329b06e33d69d384c2441dfa0ffa1","tid":22553,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T13:33:59.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（Gigi）與台灣型男張孝全近日齊出席NET-A-PORTER與MR PORTER合辦的酒會。穿鬆身裙登場的Gigi略見「肚凸凸」，她否認再有喜，更搞笑表示是未去洗手間而已；張孝全則直言若碰到真命天女也有可能閃婚。<br />\n<br />\n梁詠琪當晚的鬆身裙有「肚凸凸」效果，問是否再有喜訊？她解釋：「沒理由吧！不是啊！是未去洗手間而已。（未夠三個月不能說？）不，我之後要到台灣及內地拍戲4個月，下年年中要繼續巡迴演唱，要專心工作先。」Gigi透露劇組明白她想多點回港探望家人，故會在4個月內給她放5次假回來，即隔半個月就可返家見一見女兒與家人。Gigi弟弟日前結婚，她因工作關係沒時間選購「姑奶裙」，要上該網店搜羅，後更獲對方相邀擔任今次活動嘉賓，她直認是該店VIP，並要分享這個實際案例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/8064ea3622089da61676da006a9a8089.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F8064ea3622089da61676da006a9a8089.jpg&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ed5184ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/8064ea3622089da61676da006a9a8089.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"a5b0828dbfbfec28c3242596cf454fc16655fbef","tid":22553,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T13:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/8064ea3622089da61676da006a9a8089.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F8064ea3622089da61676da006a9a8089.jpg&h=c74d9628&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6a5202cf2b6a8a3c9263b8dab69ae64df06c254","tid":22553,"uid":5282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T13:38:08.000Z","msg":"西班牙藉老公呢？"},{"pid":"38a1a52463a8df6a0f2eb14943504b03e43ee2eb","tid":22553,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T13:42:05.000Z","msg":"明知未夠三個月唔會講<br />\nd記者就咪on99問啦"},{"pid":"f2c503b009502506bf39c136d3ec9d1091531f6f","tid":22553,"uid":34311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明知未夠三個月唔會講<br />\nd記者就咪on99問啦</blockquote><br />\n一把年紀仲生得出咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0d105641c8fd09e680f7c6c33934a83fe41a17","tid":22553,"uid":44363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/8064ea3622089da61676da006a9a8089.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F8064ea3622089da61676da006a9a8089.jpg&h=c74d9628&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩屌成個阿嬸咁嘅"},{"pid":"a4f722e376aab30f3750755125b428f9382a5ca6","tid":22553,"uid":27685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:45:39.000Z","msg":"冇西班牙藉老公Sergio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb29ef7ee6b6eea892d3cac4500356ef079ec653","tid":22553,"uid":43285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:46:42.000Z","msg":"做男人做到種馬咁"},{"pid":"4aa1ae1054e396ea042043baada073439a5b9900","tid":22553,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Rar0VWH.gif?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRar0VWH.gif%3F&h=e5dc415e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c113af25c03d185332ecfd83ca0d3cdf41d8c10","tid":22553,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848eaf9d55b03a9ace54b6b419007de9ee45eac1","tid":22553,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6456da8d68f2107713f8bdccae5d47fa28a547","tid":22553,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:59:27.000Z